Commercial Facilities Gets Standard Chartered Loan, KUNA Says

-- B y   D a h l i a   K h o l a i f
-- 
2011-04-20T12:09:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/commercial-facilities-gets-standard-chartered-loan-kuna-says.html
Commercial Facilities Co. (FACIL) , a
Kuwaiti consumer finance company, completed a $45 million term
loan facility from   Standard Chartered Plc (STAN) , state-run news
agency  KUNA  reported, citing a statement from the company.  The Kuwaiti company will use the loan to finance operations
and increase its consumer loans portfolio, Chairman Abdullah al- Humaidhi said, according to KUNA.  Editor: Peter Branton  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dahlia Kholaif in Kuwait at 
 dkholaif@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  